Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たまには  こんなのもいいねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.52,Default,Pin,0,0,0,,It's nice to let loose like this every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,のんきなもんだと思ってるんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.03,Default,Pin,0,0,0,,You probably think we're the most carefree people on earth, don't you?
